^ Rea, Alison (August 5, 1996). "Can Art Ryan Move the Rock?". Bloomberg Businessweek. Retrieved 12 December 2011. 
^ "Arthur F. Ryan". Rutgers University. Archived from the original on 27 June 2010. Retrieved 12 December 2011. 







 
